### Key Material Information (Appendix 2A - Quotation Application):  
- **Securities Issued:** 1,092,679,329 ordinary fully paid shares (CHM)  
- **Issue Price:** AUD 0.004 per share  
- **Reason:** Tranche 2 of placement announced 20 May 2025, approved by shareholders 23 July 2025.  
- **Total Post-Issue Ordinary Shares on Issue:** 3,107,873,478 (CHM)  
- **Pending Issuances (from Appendix 3B):**  
  - 1,650,000,000 options (expiring 31 Mar 2026, exercise price AUD 0.004)  
  - 25,000,000 options (expiring 31 Jul 2028, exercise price AUD 0.008)  
  - 1,650,000,000 contingent options (expiring 31 Aug 2026, exercise price AUD 0.005)  
  - 393,012,754 ordinary shares (to be issued).  

**No further material information identified.**
